{"word":"G1392 - δοξάζω - doxázō - dox-ad'-zo - Glorify","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δοξάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">doxázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dox-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Glorify</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மகிமைப்படுத்து, புகழ், மேன்மைப்படுத்து, உயர்த்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to think, suppose, be of opinion."},{"paragraph":"2. to praise, extol, magnify, celebrate"},{"paragraph":"3. to honor, do honor to, hold in honor"},{"paragraph":"4. to make glorious, adorn with lustre, clothe with splendor"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1391 - δόξα - dóxa - dox'-ah/1391\">G1391</a>; to <i>render</i> (or <i>esteem</i>) <i>glorious</i> (in a wide application): - (make) glorify (-ious), full of (have) glory, honour, magnify.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1380/1380\">G1380</a>, <a href=\"#/G1391/1391\">G1391</a>, <a href=\"#/G1392/1392\">G1392</a>, <a href=\"#/G1740/1740\">G1740</a>, <a href=\"#/G1741/1741\">G1741</a>, <a href=\"#/G3861/3861\">G3861</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888/4888\">G4888</a>"}]}